        <li>“Using the Major Field Test-Business as an Assessment Tool and Impetus for Program Improvement,” with Floyd Duncan, Ed Sexton, and Cliff West, <i>Journal of College Teaching and Learning,</i> 2008.</li> 
       </ol> 
